episodes.title: 'my obsessive ex is in a cult’
episodes.description: Hiiiii! How would you feel if your ex called you yearly like clockwork… from a “self-help retreat”? Our secret sharer has moved on, but her curiosity has got the better of her. We also discuss enemies, frenemies, and ‘acquain-emies’. Big thanks to Kiehl’s for making this episode possible. Shooshies, if you want to break up with breakouts, jump on kiehls.com.au and add to your skincare routine. And, shout-out to Materialistics hitting cinemas on June 12. Got a secret to spill? Easy peasy! Head to everybodyhasasecret.com.au and submit it anonymously. This show is only as good as the secrets that are submitted, so keep ‘em coming! Your hosts of ‘everybody has a secret’ are Annabelle Lee ( @annabe11e1ee ) and Louis Hanson ( @louishanson ). This episode was produced by Ruby Hall and executive-produced by Lucy Hunt. Catch us on socials! @everybodyhasasecretpod on Instagram and @everybodyhasasecret on TikTok. Get our weekly newsletter, Ask Us in your inbox every Friday! See you next Friday, we love ya guts for listening!
